@startuml Sequence_Community

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Community API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

== Create Discussion ==
User -> Client: Click create discussion
Client -> Client: Fill discussion form
Client -> API: POST /api/community/discussions
API -> API: Validate data
API -> DB: Create discussion
DB --> API: Discussion created
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show discussion

== Reply to Discussion ==
User -> Client: View discussion
User -> Client: Enter reply
Client -> API: POST /api/community/discussions/:id/replies
API -> DB: Create reply
DB --> API: Reply created
API --> Client: Return reply
Client --> User: Display reply

== Review Product ==
User -> Client: Click review product
Client -> Client: Fill review form
Client -> API: POST /api/products/:id/reviews
API -> DB: Create review
DB --> API: Review created
API -> DB: Update product rating
DB --> API: Rating updated
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show review

== View Discussions ==
User -> Client: View product page
Client -> API: GET /api/community/discussions?productId=:id
API -> DB: Get discussions
DB --> API: Discussions list
API --> Client: Return discussions
Client --> User: Display discussions

@enduml

